      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a solid choice for someone looking for a reliable project or a budget-friendly daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable dings, some fading paint on the roof, and a few spots of surface rust. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need some suspension work and a thorough tune-up in the near future to ensure long-term reliability. The interior is functional but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It's a dependable car that simply needs a bit of attention to bring it back to its best.",
