    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I am so incredibly sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to fall in love with it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve totally babied it from day one. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor, seriously not a single scratch or speck of dust! If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, you\u2019ve found your match. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
