    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional E46 M3, a definitive example of atmospheric performance. At its heart lies the S54 inline-six, featuring a 3.2L displacement, dual-VANOS variable valve timing, and individual throttle bodies for razor-sharp response. This unit maintains factory compression across all cylinders and has received comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a bespoke VANOS rattle kit installation. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides tactile engagement, feeding power through a reinforced rear subframe to the M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is preserved with OEM-spec bushings and dampers, ensuring the original chassis kinematics remain uncompromised. The exterior is free of marring or rock chips, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather with no bolster fatigue. A comprehensive dossier of service records accompanies this mechanically flawless specimen.",
